      propertyPath: testText
      value: "Welcome Experiment #34, as you can tell the surgery was a resounding
        success. We were able to put your brain inside of your hips with minimal
        damage. It only took us 33 patients to figure it out! \n\nYou probably have
        no clue to move that knew body of yours, so just remember to use WASD or
        Arrow Keys to move, Space to jump/wall jump, and Left Shift to sprint. You
        will be able to 'sense' whatever you are touching, but nothing more. Find
        the path to the next level. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
